# Controllers

Read [docs/RAILS_STYLEGUIDE.md](../../docs/RAILS_STYLEGUIDE.md), [docs/DOMAIN.md](../../docs/DOMAIN.md).

- Thin controllers: `authenticate_user!`, strong params, call model domain methods for rules.
- Match `EventsController`, `FriendshipsController` patterns.
- Files under 150 lines.
- Do not run commands unless explicitly requested.
